data.title: Dennys fan
data.text: I love Dennys. Most Dennys have such nice waiters, so friendly and ready to help you ALWAYS with a smile on their face, it makes me want to work there. There's quite a variety of food and they have the 55+menu which makes the delicious menus more healthy. Also it's cheap! I love you Dennys!!!!!

data.title: Poor, Poor Service
data.text: I can't speak for the actual food as we didn't get served. We went in and there was a big line of people but many available tables. Another frustrated customer then told us that there was a problem with the cash registers and everyone has been waiting for it to be fixed for the last 30 minutes. During this time, they wouldn't seat anyone. There was even a customer there that just wanted a coffee to go and couldn't get it. If they aren't prepared in times like that, I wasn't waiting there.

data.title: Excellent service
data.text: Nous sommes aller plusieurs fois pour le petit déjeuner entre 9h et midi et toujours bon accueil avec des efforts pour nous satisfaire et nous expliquer le menu. Toujours du monde ambiance hispanique et puis le choix de la carte est suffisant.
